<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your OTP Code - ZapWallet</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap');
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #009689 0%, #00c4b4 50%, #ffd8af 100%);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 150, 137, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .email-container:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: #009689;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            right: -10%;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: rgba(255, 216, 175, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        
        .header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -30%;
            left: -10%;
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
            background: rgba(255, 216, 175, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        
        .logo-container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }
        
        .logo-subtitle {
            font-size: 15px;
            opacity: 0.95;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 45px 40px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            color: #009689;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .message {
            color: #4a5568;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .otp-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #009689 0%, #00c4b4 100%);
            padding: 35px 25px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 35px 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 3px solid #ffd8af;
        }
        
        .otp-container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, rgba(255, 216, 175, 0.2), transparent);
            transform: rotate(45deg);
            animation: shine 3s infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes shine {
            0% { transform: translateX(-100%) translateY(-100%) rotate(45deg); }
            100% { transform: translateX(100%) translateY(100%) rotate(45deg); }
        }
        
        .otp-label {
            color: #ffd8af;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: white;
            letter-spacing: 12px;
            text-shadow: 2px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .validity {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd8af 0%, #ffead4 100%);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border: 2px solid #ffd8af;
        }
        
        .validity-text {
            color: #009689;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .validity-text strong {
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .warning {
            background: #fff5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid #fc8181;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .warning-text {
            color: #c53030;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .help-section {
            background: #f7fafc;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px dashed #009689;
        }
        
        .help-title {
            color: #009689;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .help-text {
            color: #4a5568;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .contact-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #009689;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .contact-button:hover {
            background: #007a6e;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 150, 137, 0.3);
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 25px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 13px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .footer-brand {
            color: #009689;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer-links {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .footer-link {
            color: #009689;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        .footer-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .security-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            background: #009689;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .icon {
            margin-right: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .divider {
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #ffd8af, transparent);
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 30px 25px;
            }
            
            .otp-code {
                font-size: 36px;
                letter-spacing: 8px;
            }
            
            .greeting {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .logo {
                font-size: 32px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo-container">
                <div class="logo">‚ö° ZapWallet</div>
                <div class="logo-subtitle">Fast, Secure, Seamless Payments</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="greeting">Hello <%= name %>,</h1>
            
            <p class="message">
                We received a request to verify your ZapWallet account. 
                Please use the One-Time Password (OTP) below to complete your verification and proceed securely with your transaction.
            </p>
            
            <div class="otp-container">
                <div class="otp-label">Your Verification Code</div>
                <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="validity">
                <div class="validity-text">‚è∞ This code expires in <strong>2 minutes</strong></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <div class="warning">
                <div class="warning-text">
                    üîí <strong>Security Alert:</strong> Never share this OTP with anyone, including ZapWallet staff. 
                    We will never ask for your OTP, PIN, or password via email, phone, or text. 
                    If you didn't request this code, please secure your account immediately.
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="help-section">
                <div class="help-title">Need Help?</div>
                <div class="help-text">
                    If you didn't request this verification or have any concerns about your account security
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="contact-button">Contact Support</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-brand">¬© 2024 ZapWallet. All rights reserved.</div>
            <div>Making digital payments simple, secure, and accessible for everyone</div>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Privacy Policy</a>
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Terms of Service</a>
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Help Center</a>
            </div>
            <div class="security-badge">
                <span class="icon">üõ°Ô∏è</span> Secured & Licensed by Bangladesh Bank
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>